song.title: Adventure at Silly Venture
song.info:
Notes from 505: "A tribute to the great Silly Venture Atari party series in Gdansk, Poland - which hopefully is going to be continued one day.
Tracked with Renoise, sample based and using 4 channels as I intended to convert it to Protracker format at some point."
Released on the [url]chiptuneswin.com[/url] bandcamp release volume 4: [url]http://chiptuneswin.bandcamp.com/album/chiptunes-win-volume-4[/url]
Also 505's soundcloud: [url]https://soundcloud.com/five-o-five[/url]
(Uploaded with permission from 505 and Chiptunes=WIN)
